# Presets

JSON under **`src/presets/`** as **SerializedGraphFile**: required `format` (`shadernoice-node-graph` or legacy `shader-composer-node-graph`), **`formatVersion: "2.0"`**, **`graph`**; optional **`audioSetup`**.

Filenames: **kebab-case**, descriptive (UI derives display title).

Adding JSON only — discovery is directory-based unless tooling changes.

If you alter the **serialized shape**, update **`serialization.ts`** + migrations + **`src/presets/README.md`**. Load/save stays on the single serialization path (`.cursor/rules/data-model/serialization.mdc`).

**Ref:** `src/presets/README.md`.
